Package org.casa.synthproxy

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArduinoCommandHandler
    Arduino Command Handler is the class that handles all commands received from CASAActuator.
    CASASynthProxy
    This is the MAIN class of the CASASynthProxy.
    Command
    This class maps a command in CASA system.
    CommandSender
    This is an abstract class that maps all basic operations in order to send commands to CASAActuator.
    CommPort
    This class maps a serial communication port that is used to communicate with CASAActuator.
    ConnectionHandler
    This class is in charge of handling commands coming from a TCP/IP connection.
    VoiceSynth
    Text synthesizer.
